creator: Excite Africa
descriptionHtml:
Excite Enterprise is a virtual marketplace for small and medium business owners. It is essentially, an online business solutions platform, where merchants get their businesses registered and organized using the books-keeping and invoicing tools and make tax remittances as well as list products and services for sale.
The provision of business and enterprise solutions bundled with marketing and branding, have a compelling attraction to buyers and users.
Excite Enterprise is a virtual marketplace for businesses with logistics for sales and a payment platform as well as buyer/seller relationship management
The Enterprise side, which contains the sales window and book-keeping help sustainably capture data, value and insights on the market as they trade
